    title: "AEM Corporation, Sr. Director of Transportation Systems Corporation, TIM Instructor, Support Lead for the EDC-5/6 Crowdsourcing Innovation",
    description: "Ms. Shah has led and contributed to FHWA, USDOT ITS JPO, FAA, and National Cooperative Highway Research Program efforts, helping public agencies improve decision-making through new technologies, tools, and processes. Ms. Shah holds a BS degree from the University of Maryland and an MS degree from the University of Texas.",
    image: vaishaliShah
  },
  {
